Title: A Roy Rogers in Franconia
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (created by), Joel Fields, Joseph Weisberg
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Dylan Baker, Brandon J. Dirden
Plot: As Paige deals with last episode's trauma, she sees her mother in a new light... and finds she has inherited some of her parents' skills. Plus, has Oleg reached his breaking point with Stan?
